<pb facs="1038358" n="1"/>
<opener><lb/>Viro Illustrissimo et Doctissimo
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petro Antonio Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>NB.</abbr></rs></opener>
<p><lb/>Siquidem <add>ob</add> rerum mearum domesticarum statu<subst><del>s</del><add>m</add></subst> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> morte
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-135542286" type="person">Parentis</rs> mei i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>utatu<subst><del>s</del><add>m</add></subst><del> mihi occasionem dedit cepi</del> pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>positum cepi, isto vacationum tempore bona cum venia
         <lb/><abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="persons" key="pers_DE-588-121843858 pers_DE-588-1253768439 pers_DE-588-1178380696"><abbr>Reff.</abbr></rs> <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs> abeundi, Te ejusdem mei
         <lb/>propositi certiorem facio, ut si qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> habe<subst><del>s</del><add>as</add></subst> mandata per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ferenda, ea mihi significes. Hanc simul <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te peto gratiam,
         <lb/>ut inclusam <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> <abbr>Ill.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118538535">Residenti</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118538543"><abbr>M.</abbr> B<unclear>r</unclear>ita<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>i<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Regis</rs>
<lb/>tradi cures aut ipse,<del> <gap/></del> si <del><gap/></del><add>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice></add>ode fieri possit, tradas veniamque
         <lb/>ab ipso exores pro me, quod libertate ab ipso mihi concessa usus
         <lb/>sim. Ignosce quoque Tu ipse libertati petitionis me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>.
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Patruelis</rs> meus jam ante tres hebdomadas hinc profectus est; eum 
         <lb/>non longe <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiis</rs> abesse spero. <del>Nondum certus sum, quo
         <lb/>die ego hinc proficiscar, forte proximo die Jovis</del> Ego con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stitui hinc abire proximo die Jovis, nisi forte impediar.</p>
<lb/><closer>Det Deus, ut feliciter redux salvum et incolumem Te
         <lb/>salutare queam. <salute>Vale et fave.</salute><dateline><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <date when="1717-05-31"/>31. Maji 1717</dateline>.</closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>